column1: #Text=So that was an amazing experience to go on that tour and to see what a championship team looks like under the competition of that ilk .
#Text=And I was then the assistant coach basically right through to London .
#Text=After London , Ben was quite happy for me to continue .
#Text=By this stage , 2011 , I 'd given up all the Villanova stuff so I concentrated just on the wheelchair and my Queensland group .
#Text=And I started to build the Queensland junior program , which featured Tom O'Neill-Thorne , Jordon Bartley , Bailey Rowland , all of those sort of players .
#Text=You probably do n't know too many of them , but ,
#Text=And three of those were in last year 's , 2013 under-23s team .
#Text=So in 2012 obviously we went to Varese then on to London for the Paras .
#Text=When I came back , Ben asked me to do the under-23s as the head coach , and asked me who I wanted as my assistant , so in the December , we , David Gould and I ...
#Text=So you selected David as your assistant ?
#Text=Yes ! Yes ! Yes ! I had a lot of dealings with David , seeing him with the Gliders .
#Text=Plus I 'd also seen him with the Adelaide Thunder .
#Text=He was coaching them for a while , and I really liked the way he worked with kids .
#Text=He 'd also done a camp with the under-23s in 2012 because I could n't attend , himself and Sonia Taylor .
#Text=What was Sonia 's previous name before she married Nick Taylor ? [ ... ]
#Text=Anyway , they did a development camp in January 2012 with the under-23s group because I could n't attend .
#Text=In the April , the Rollers had gone off to Verase , and there was an opportunity to go to Dubai with the under-23/25 age group .
#Text=So David and Sonia took them to Dubai and did a good job with them , a really great job with them .
#Text=So the job for the 23s came up in November 2012 .
#Text=And then was asked who I would want as my assistants , and Ben told me who the other applicants were and I told him , yep , happy with both of those .
#Text=So we took the under-23s group in December .
#Text=Had a couple of camps in the first part of 2013 , getting ready for the world championships in Turkey in September .
#Text=At that stage we got to about June , and the head coach for the Gliders came up as a full time position .
#Text=They had n't had a full-time coach before .
#Text=Tom Kyle addresses his players at the 2014 Women 's World Wheelchair Basketball Championship .
